  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana (APY). Here's how you can do it:\n\n1. **Visit the Bank or Post Office**: Go to the bank or post office where you opened your APY account.\n\n2. **Fill Out the Nominee Change Form**: Request the nominee change form from the bank or post office. Fill out the form with the updated nominee details.\n\n3. **Submit the Form**: Submit the filled-out form to the bank or post office. They will process your request and update the nominee details in their records.\n\n4. **Online Method**: If your bank offers online services for APY, you may be able to change the nominee details through their online portal. Log in to your account, navigate to the APY section, and look for an option to update nominee details. Follow the instructions provided.\n\n5. **Confirmation**: After submitting your request, you should receive a confirmation from the bank or post office once the nominee details have been updated.\n\nRemember to keep your contact information updated with the bank or post office to receive important communications about your APY account.",
